data.description: QUICK CLOSE & BETTER THAN NEW, You'll Love this Home - It Sparkles! 3 Yrs Young on an oversized lot, Lovely w 1st Flr Master EnSuite is just what you're looking for. Enter through the Covered Porch to an Open Floorplan. Relax in the Spacious Family Rm w gas Fireplace to curl up in front of on chilly fall & winter evenings. Gather in the Kitchen as you prepare meals like a pro w granite countertops, Island w overhang for seating & serving, Double Ovens, Cooktop & Spacious Pantry. You'll be proud to serve in the bright Formal Dining Rm w wainscoting & tray ceiling. Breakfast Rm leads to Screened Porch & adjacent Patio to enjoy the outdoors in your Fenced-in flat, usable backyard complete w Shed. Plenty of space for volleyball, badminton, croquet, etc. The 2nd floor greets you w a Generous Bonus Rm, large & close to 3 bdrms, 2 full baths. Side load Garage, this also has an oversized driveway to park extra cars. This home has it all. Relocation - No DD$ required, home has already been assessed, great condition. Sellers' relo is your opportunity to own this Great Home. BE IN BY THE HOLIDAYS! Must See. *Pictures are not in correct sequence due to MLS system transition*
